name: Tic-tac-toe
body:
### Welcome to GitHub Pages.
 In order to run on your github repository use the following commands for noval users. After your page is generated, you can check out the new branch:

```
$ cd your_repo_root/repo_name
$ git fetch origin
$ git checkout gh-pages
```

If you're using the GitHub for Mac, simply sync your repository and you'll see the new branch.
